snippet.title: Scoober Splat! - Rough Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Scoober Splat! is Dead by Daylight meets Among Us! Chase your friends in a team-based game of tag, where everyone powers up between rounds! 
Click here to play in browser: https://scoobersplat.com/play
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/nobloatstudios
Join our discord : https://discord.gg/tDWhzMekgJ
Steam page for the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1601830/Scoober_Splat/
